 {"text": "year-over-year, primarily reflecting a 7.1 percent increase in the volume of OEC on rent and a 0.4 percent rental", "bbox": [143.8, 1115.3, 1094.0, 1136.1]}, {"text": "rate increase. We believe that the increase in the volume of OEC on rent reflects improving demand in many of", "bbox": [143.8, 1140.3, 1094.2, 1161.1]}, {"text": "our core markets. Equipment rentals represented 86 percent of total revenues in 2017. On a segment basis,", "bbox": [143.8, 1165.3, 1094.1, 1186.1]}, {"text": "equipment rentals represented 85 percent and 92 percent of total revenues for general rentals and trench, power", "bbox": [143.8, 1190.3, 1094.2, 1211.1]}, {"text": "and pump, respectively. General rentals equipment rentals increased $561, or 13.5 percent, as compared to 2016,", "bbox": [143.8, 1215.3, 1094.2, 1236.2]}, {"text": "primarily reflecting a 16.9 percent increase in the volume of OEC on rent, which includes the impact of the NES", "bbox": [143.8, 1240.3, 1094.3, 1261.2]}, {"text": "and Neff acquisitions. On a pro forma basis including the standalone, pre-acquisition results of NES and Neff,", "bbox": [143.8, 1265.3, 1094.1, 1286.2]}, {"text": "the volume of OEC on rent increased 5.5 percent. We believe that the increase in the volume of OEC on rent", "bbox": [143.8, 1290.3, 1094.1, 1311.2]}, {"text": "reflects improving demand in many of our core markets. Trench, power and pump equipment rentals increased", "bbox": [143.8, 1315.3, 1094.0, 1336.2]}, {"text": "$213, or 27.5 percent, primarily reflecting a 34.9 percent increase in the volume of OEC on rent. Trench, power", "bbox": [143.8, 1340.4, 1094.2, 1361.2]}, {"text": "and pump average OEC increased 14.3 percent. The increase in the volume of OEC on rent significantly", "bbox": [143.8, 1365.4, 1093.9, 1386.2]}, {"text": "exceeded the increase in average OEC primarily due to improved performance in our Pump Solutions region. The", "bbox": [143.8, 1390.4, 1094.2, 1411.2]}, {"text": "improvement in the Pump Solutions region primarily reflected growth in revenue from i) upstream oil and gas", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.4, 1094.2, 1436.2]}, {"text": "40", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}